P'Hill

755
00:47:45,950 --> 00:47:48,620
Ada orang cuba mendekati P'Johan?

756
00:47:50,660 --> 00:47:52,110
Ada

757
00:47:52,410 --> 00:47:54,110
Tapi saya halau mereka semua

758
