00:50:52,660 --> 00:50:54,680
(Saya di depan asrama kamu, turunlah)

808
00:50:54,690 --> 00:50:56,550
(Bukankah saya sudah katakan jangan pergi ke mana-mana?)

809
00:50:58,000 --> 00:50:59,740
Ter

810
00:51:17,480 --> 00:51:19,220
Kamu mahu bawa saya ke mana

811
00:51:19,240 --> 00:51:21,220
Kamu tidur di sini

812
00:51:25,760 --> 00:51:27,420
Pakai baju saya.

813
00:51:27,470 --> 00:51:28,360
Perasaan melindungi begitu kuat.

814
00:51:28,360 --> 00:51:29,550
Adakah itu jaket teman lelaki masa depan kamu?

815
00:51:29,580 --> 00:51:30,470
Jangan cakap lagi.

816
00:51:30,490 --> 00:51:31,840
